standard function for clustering:
1. is not destructive
2. returns a modified util.Coords object
3. takes only the util.Coords as a normal argument
4. keyword arguments are described as:

use_default_centers:False  -> uses cluster centers provided in util.Coords object
iterations:10  -> number of required iterations
anim_obj:None -> an animation object that may be used. if provided, animation steps will be pushed to it.

more objects might be added if it will be nescesary
